  spellID: 2
  spellName: Grandpas Spell
  spellIcon: {fileID: 1359254230896072486, guid: 653bd11cf40c09a4d8d4d783bb502e45,
    type: 3}
  loreDescription: 'Dear Marty and Mary:

    I hope this finds you well. I know
    that I haven''t been easy to talk to in the past few years, but I hope to remedy
    that. I have constructed this spell so that I may help you, even long after I
    am gone. I love you so much, you two.

    - Grandpa'
  mechanicDescription: Envision a button, labelled 'Q'. Now, whilst holding this
    book, imagine pressing that button. A friendly and familial apparition you know
    should appear and offer you wisdom.
  spellPrefab: {fileID: 2363184364508103593, guid: f03b7643243bfef4dbc2729bbe2ee53c,
    type: 3}
